version_description:
• Find the Payout ID for each settled transaction within your transaction details or your daily payout report. Your Payout ID can be used to find the payout in your bank statement, for example: SUMUP PID1234.

• For users with “Advanced Mode” enabled, product descriptions beginning with numerical characters and followed by alphabetical ones are now ordered automatically in the product catalogue.

• Find the Payout ID for each settled transaction within your transaction details or your daily payout report. Your Payout ID can be used to find the payout in your bank statement, for example: SUMUP PID1234.

• For users with “Advanced Mode” enabled, product descriptions beginning with numerical characters and followed by alphabetical ones are now ordered automatically in the product catalogue.

• Fixes the icon displayed for successful payments in the Sales History.

In version 1.67.1:
• Find the Payout ID for each settled transaction within your transaction details or your daily payout report. Your Payout ID can be used to find the payout in your bank statement, for example: SUMUP PID1234.
• For users with “Advanced Mode” enabled, product descriptions beginning with numerical characters and followed by alphabetical ones are now ordered automatically in the product catalogue.

• Fixes the icon displayed for successful payments in the Sales History.

In version 1.67.1:
• Find the Payout ID for each settled transaction within your transaction details or your daily payout report. Your Payout ID can be used to find the payout in your bank statement, for example: SUMUP PID1234.
• For users with “Advanced Mode” enabled, product descriptions beginning with numerical characters and followed by alphabetical ones are now ordered automatically in the product catalogue.

• Add option to reveal password when logging in
• Minor fixes and stability improvements

• Add option to reveal password when logging in
• Minor fixes and stability improvements

• New languages added: Greek, Norwegian, Finnish, Slovenian and Lithuanian. If your phone is set to one of these languages, the app will be displayed accordingly in this language.
• You can now see the amount that has been deducted from a payout for refunded transactions.
• Fixes an issue that would display a settlement card for refunded transactions in the Sales History.

• New languages added: Greek, Norwegian, Finnish, Slovenian and Lithuanian. If your phone is set to one of these languages, the app will be displayed accordingly in this language.
• You can now see the amount that has been deducted from a payout for refunded transactions.
• Fixes an issue that would display a settlement card for refunded transactions in the Sales History.

• Support for iPhone X

In this update, we are introducing the new challenges section on the refer a friend tab! You can earn extra rewards when there's a challenge available and track your progress towards completing it.

We are proud to present the all new SumUp app!
Faster, easier to navigate and more powerful than ever.

All changes in a nutshell:
* Beautiful, intuitive design
* Bottom navigation for easier access to features
* Partial refunds
* Performance improvements
* Bug fixes
